            We have just completed an install of Piwik in a medium traffic site (10,000 visits a day), and the client emailed just a single 3 letter word back. Wow. Piwik will be continued to be rolled out through the portfolio of sites (total about 18 million visits a year).            <small>
                <span rel="author">James</span> 
                , CTO, Media company w/ hundreds of websites                             </small>
