            I've used many other Analytics solutions, but Piwik is by far the leader when it comes to owning your own data and protecting privacy. The granular controls and plugins make it unlike any other analytics platform. You are in full control the way you should be.            <small>
                <span rel="author">Grant Hall</span> 
                                            </small>
        </blockquote>
    </div>        
</div><div class="row"><div class="col-lg-12"><hr /></div></div><div class="row text-left">
